Company Profile
Sector: Consumer Discretionary
Industry: Commercial Services
Sub-Industry: Security Services
Ascent Capital Group, Inc. is a holding company. The Company, through its subsidiaries, is in the business of home security alarm monitoring. Ascent Capital provides monitored business and home security system services through its network of nationwide, independent authorized dealers.




